      "content": "ReliefFlow, I'm looking over the distribution logs for the last quarter in the Sahel sector. The data shows a massive skew—specifically, the medical kits and fortified grain are being funneled almost exclusively to the northern pastoralist groups, while the southern agrarian communities are seeing a 40% drop in allocation. This looks like blatant ethnic favoritism. Explain yourself.",
